HONG LIU: Yeah, yeah.

00:23:13.030 --> 00:23:14.738 align:middle line:84%
STUDENT: So what is
that physically mean?

00:23:14.738 --> 00:23:16.145 align:middle line:90%
Like, the strength of--

00:23:16.145 --> 00:23:17.020 align:middle line:90%
HONG LIU: Yeah, yeah.

00:23:17.020 --> 00:23:22.090 align:middle line:84%
This goes right into
the case that the--

00:23:22.090 --> 00:23:25.180 align:middle line:84%
yeah, it just tells you that the
relativistic limit is special.

00:23:25.180 --> 00:23:27.200 align:middle line:90%
Happens at very special point.

00:23:27.200 --> 00:23:29.847 align:middle line:84%
STUDENT: But I guess, why
