00:23:40.660 --> 00:23:42.720 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, yeah.

00:23:42.720 --> 00:23:45.280 align:middle line:84%
It's just like when you choose
some special parameters,

00:23:45.280 --> 00:23:50.730 align:middle line:84%
then you can have a
