00:23:50.730 --> 00:23:51.470 align:middle line:90%
Other questions?

00:23:51.470 --> 00:23:52.322 align:middle line:90%
Yes?

00:23:52.322 --> 00:23:53.780 align:middle line:84%
STUDENT: Yeah, so
