00:24:29.008 --> 00:24:29.630 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:24:29.630 --> 00:24:35.870 align:middle line:84%
And actually, the breakthrough
of the phase transition

00:24:35.870 --> 00:24:38.660 align:middle line:84%
in condensed matter
physics to understand

00:24:38.660 --> 00:24:40.550 align:middle line:84%
what phase transition
is really about

00:24:40.550 --> 00:24:43.190 align:middle line:84%
and describe the behavior
of the phase transition,

00:24:43.190 --> 00:24:46.850 align:middle line:84%
and precisely coincided with
