00:24:46.850 --> 00:24:50.130 align:middle line:84%
And yeah, actually,
increased our understanding

00:24:50.130 --> 00:24:51.420 align:middle line:90%
of quantum field theory, yeah.

00:24:51.420 --> 00:24:54.270 align:middle line:90%


