terms of a and a dagger.

00:42:04.950 --> 00:42:12.010 align:middle line:90%


00:42:12.010 --> 00:42:14.770 align:middle line:84%
And then you can just use a and
a dagger because a and a dagger

00:42:14.770 --> 00:42:15.820 align:middle line:90%
essentially--

00:42:15.820 --> 00:42:18.580 align:middle line:84%
they are fundamental
building block

00:42:18.580 --> 00:42:20.200 align:middle line:90%
