00:42:20.200 --> 00:42:23.810 align:middle line:84%
And then you can also use that
to build the Hilbert space.

00:42:23.810 --> 00:42:28.480 align:middle line:84%
So the Hilbert space is
defined by the lowest

00:42:28.480 --> 00:42:42.940 align:middle line:84%
state is annihilated by a,
and then the higher state

00:42:42.940 --> 00:42:49.170 align:middle line:84%
obtained by acting a
dagger on the ground state.

00:42:49.170 --> 00:42:52.020 align:middle line:90%
So this is your full theory.

00:42:52.020 --> 00:42:54.510 align:middle line:90%
So this is your full theory.

00:42:54.510 --> 00:43:00.220 align:middle line:84%
And so now, now you can
compute anything in this theory

00:43:00.220 --> 00:43:04.390 align:middle line:84%
just with those knowledge,
just with those knowledge.

