00:47:49.130 --> 00:47:51.470 align:middle line:84%
So here, we start with
a classical system,

00:47:51.470 --> 00:47:52.820 align:middle line:90%
and then we quantize it.

00:47:52.820 --> 00:47:58.400 align:middle line:84%
And the quantum system is a
