00:47:59.420 --> 00:48:01.640 align:middle line:84%
They're essentially
intrinsically quantum.

00:48:01.640 --> 00:48:03.410 align:middle line:90%
And yeah.

00:48:03.410 --> 00:48:04.370 align:middle line:90%
Like spin.

00:48:04.370 --> 00:48:07.550 align:middle line:84%
Spin is an intrinsic
in quantum, so yeah.

00:48:07.550 --> 00:48:08.428 align:middle line:90%
Yes?

00:48:08.428 --> 00:48:10.970 align:middle line:84%
STUDENT: This question is to do
