The vacuum state
here is based on--

00:49:11.910 --> 00:49:16.080 align:middle line:90%
is coming from the energy.

00:49:16.080 --> 00:49:19.590 align:middle line:84%
So once we solve x
and p, and then we

00:49:19.590 --> 00:49:22.110 align:middle line:84%
