00:49:26.310 --> 00:49:27.750 align:middle line:90%
that satisfy this equation.

00:49:27.750 --> 00:49:28.260 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:49:28.260 --> 00:49:30.810 align:middle line:84%
And then from there, you
can find other states.

00:49:30.810 --> 00:49:32.315 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, yeah.

